{"tid":698414,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"遇著呢啲上司慘過食屎xx(","createTime":"2018-06-11T16:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T16:22:48.000Z","uid":69837,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d82d6170221b2329820f351efcc1112940f6c992","tid":698414,"uid":69837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T16:11:44.000Z","msg":"小弟由畢業到依家工作左年幾到<br />\n工作一直表現良好<br />\n但同上司關係一向麻麻 而上司亦出左名賤<br />\n就係因為咁而打算轉工<br />\n自從上司知道我有轉工呢個念頭 就對我更加衰 <br />\n就係幾個月之前 我去左一間A公司見工<br />\n最近唔知點解上司知道左我去過A公司見工<br />\n今日就叫左我入房傾左陣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :上司  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你係米之前去過A公司見工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我都係聽翻黎架咋，A公司話覺得你做唔到野，仲同左全行既公司講叫佢地唔好請你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 會唔會有啲咩誤會？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我都唔清楚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出左房之後 小弟諗唔明 <br />\n明明我淨係係呢間公司做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦一直表現良好 點解無啦啦會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要封殺我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 勿相認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caea7fbe416c7c52f7bce74caa7a77c2650974b","tid":698414,"uid":69837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dfb412b84cb5c66d926c01e69ffd2454fcea444"